<!-- app/views/profile/coding.html.erb -->
<% provide(:title, "Coding") %>
<header class="my-banner-section coding-banner d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" id="home">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Coding</h1>
    <p class="lead">Where creativity meets logic.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section id="coding-content" class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Coding & Computer Science</h2>
    <p>I am a Computer Science major with a passion for coding and software development. Over the course of my studies, I’ve taken various classes that have solidified my skills and deepened my understanding of programming.</p>
    <p>I am proficient in **Visual Basic**, **Python**, and **Java**, as well as web technologies like **HTML/CSS**, which form the foundation of my web development expertise. These skills have enabled me to design and build engaging, responsive websites and applications.</p>
    <p>Currently, I’m expanding my knowledge by taking classes in **Ruby on Rails**, **JavaScript/jQuery**, and **JSON**. These courses are equipping me with the latest web development tools and techniques to build robust, data-driven applications.</p>
    <p>My academic journey and personal projects have prepared me to tackle complex programming challenges, and I’m excited to continue learning and evolving as a developer.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="text-center my-4">
  <%= link_to at101_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" do %>
    <i class="fas fa-lock me-2"></i>
    My Creative Code AT101 Projects
  <% end %>
  <p class="text-muted small mt-2 mb-0">
    Area for weekly assignments
  </p>
</div>


<!-- Explore More buttons to other sections -->
<section id="explore-coding" class="py-5 bg-light text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Explore More</h2>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Explore navigation">
      <%= link_to coding_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg active" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-code me-2"></i>Coding
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to design_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-paint-brush me-2"></i>Design
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to photography_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-camera me-2"></i>Photography
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to music_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-music me-2"></i>Music
      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

